            <html:p>We say that a <fr:link href="/008C/" title="Time-dependent vector field" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/008C/" display-uri="008C" type="local">vector field</fr:link> <html:em>generates</html:em> a <fr:link href="/008B/" title="Probablity density path" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/008B/" display-uri="008B" type="local">probability density path</fr:link> if the <fr:link href="/008D/" title="Flow" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/008D/" display-uri="008D" type="local">flow</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[v_t]]></fr:tex> satisfies
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[p_t = [\phi _t]_* p_{0},]]></fr:tex>
where
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[[\phi _t]_*p_{0}(x) = p_{0}(\phi _t^{-1}(x)) \det \left [ \frac {\partial  \phi _t^{-1} }{\partial  x}(x) \right ].  ]]></fr:tex></html:p>
